title: Moneyline Monaco - Week 2 NFL Bets: Bears-Packers, Dolphins-Ravens, Panthers-Giants, Colts-Jaguars
itunes:title: Moneyline Monaco - Week 2 NFL Bets: Bears-Packers, Dolphins-Ravens, Panthers-Giants, Colts-Jaguars
description:
Alex Monaco shares his best bets for week 2 of the NFL season including Tua Tagovailoa and the Dolphins heading to Baltimore for a matchup with Lamar Jackson and the Ravens, Baker Mayfield leading his Panthers into New York to take on Saquon Barkley and the Giants, and Aaron Rodgers and the Packers looking to rebound from a tough week 1 against the Vikings as they face off with the Chicago Bears in Lambeau Field. #volume #herd #colincowherd
